---
// Article 2.4: EPF/KWSP
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../../components/Footer.astro';
import Breadcrumb from '../../../components/panduan-rakyat/Breadcrumb';

const articleData = {
  sectionNumber: '02',
  sectionTitle: 'Work and Employment',
  sectionIcon: '💼',
  articleTitle: 'Employees Provident Fund (EPF/KWSP)',
  articleDescription: 'Retirement savings, withdrawals, and account management',
  colorRgb: '37, 99, 235',
  lastUpdated: 'March 2026',
};

const simpleContent = `
  <h2 id="what-is-epf">What is EPF?</h2>
  <p>EPF (Employees Provident Fund) or KWSP (Kumpulan Wang Simpanan Pekerja) is a retirement savings scheme for workers in Malaysia. A portion of your salary goes into your EPF account every month.</p>
  
  <h2 id="who-contributes">Who contributes?</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>You:</strong> 11% of your salary goes to EPF</li>
    <li><strong>Your employer:</strong> 12-13% of your salary goes to EPF</li>
    <li>Both amounts go into YOUR account</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="when-can-withdraw">When can you withdraw?</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>👴 Age 55 (full withdrawal)</li>
    <li>🏠 To buy a house (Account 1)</li>
    <li>🎓 For education (Account 2)</li>
    <li>🏥 For medical treatment</li>
    <li>✈️ When leaving Malaysia permanently</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="how-to-check">How to check your EPF:</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Online:</strong> Register at kwsp.gov.my</li>
    <li><strong>App:</strong> Download i-Akaun app</li>
    <li><strong>Phone:</strong> Call 03-8922 6000</li>
    <li><strong>In-person:</strong> Visit EPF counter with IC</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="important-numbers">Important numbers:</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>EPF Hotline:</strong> 03-8922 6000</li>
    <li><strong>Website:</strong> kwsp.gov.my</li>
    <li><strong>WhatsApp:</strong> 017-555 9900</li>
  </ul>
`;

const detailedContent = `
  <h2 id="overview">Overview</h2>
  <p>The Employees Provident Fund (EPF), known in Malay as Kumpulan Wang Simpanan Pekerja (KWSP), is a compulsory retirement savings scheme for employees in Malaysia. Established in 1951, EPF manages retirement savings for over 15 million members.</p>

  <h2 id="contribution-rates">Contribution Rates (2026)</h2>
  <table class="w-full border-collapse border border-border my-4">
    <thead>
      <tr class="bg-muted">
        <th class="border border-border p-3 text-left">Monthly Salary</th>
        <th class="border border-border p-3 text-left">Employee Contribution</th>
        <th class="border border-border p-3 text-left">Employer Contribution</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td class="border border-border p-3">≤ RM5,000</td>
        <td class="border border-border p-3">11% (or 9% if opted)</td>
        <td class="border border-border p-3">13%</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td class="border border-border p-3">> RM5,000</td>
        <td class="border border-border p-3">11% (or 9% if opted)</td>
        <td class="border border-border p-3">12%</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td class="border border-border p-3">Foreign workers</td>
        <td class="border border-border p-3">11% (optional)</td>
        <td class="border border-border p-3">12%</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2 id="account-structure">Account Structure (Effective 2024)</h2>
  <h3>Account 1 (75%) - Primary Account</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>For retirement</li>
    <li>Can withdraw at age 55, 60, or 65</li>
    <li>Limited withdrawal options before retirement</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Account 2 (20%) - Secondary Account</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>For housing, education, medical</li>
    <li>More flexible withdrawal options</li>
    <li>Can be used for Account 1 purposes</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Account 3 (5%) - Flexible Account (Akaun Fleksibel)</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>For any purpose</li>
    <li>Can withdraw anytime</li>
    <li>Minimum balance: RM500</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="how-to-register">How to Register for EPF</h2>
  <h3>For Employees:</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Your employer should register you within 7 days of employment</li>
    <li>Fill Form KWSP 1 (Employee Registration Form)</li>
    <li>Provide IC/passport copy</li>
    <li>Receive your EPF number (starts with numbers, e.g., 1234567890)</li>
  </ol>

  <h3>For Self-Employed (Voluntary):</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Visit nearest EPF branch</li>
    <li>Fill Form KWSP 1A</li>
    <li>Bring IC and proof of income</li>
    <li>Start contributing at your chosen amount</li>
  </ol>

  <h2 id="withdrawal-options">Withdrawal Options</h2>
  <h3>Full Withdrawal:</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>✅ Age 55 (50% Account 1 + all Account 2 & 3)</li>
    <li>✅ Age 60 (remaining 50% Account 1)</li>
    <li>✅ Leaving Malaysia permanently (after 1 year)</li>
    <li>✅ Incapacitation (medical certification required)</li>
    <li>✅ Death (by nominated beneficiaries)</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Partial Withdrawal (Account 2):</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>🏠 House purchase or mortgage reduction</li>
    <li>🎓 Education (member or children)</li>
    <li>🏥 Medical treatment (critical illnesses)</li>
    <li>👶 Maternity/paternity expenses</li>
    <li>🕌 Hajj pilgrimage (up to RM10,000)</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Flexible Withdrawal (Account 3):</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Any purpose, anytime</li>
    <li>Minimum withdrawal: RM50</li>
    <li>Maintain minimum RM500 balance</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="how-to-check-balance">How to Check Your EPF Balance</h2>
  <h3>Online (i-Akaun):</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Register at <strong>epf.gov.my</strong></li>
    <li>Click "Register" for i-Akaun</li>
    <li>Enter EPF number, IC, and phone number</li>
    <li>Receive activation code via SMS</li>
    <li>Login and view your statement</li>
  </ol>

  <h3>Mobile App:</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Download "i-Akaun" from App Store or Google Play</li>
    <li>Register with your details</li>
    <li>Check balance anytime, anywhere</li>
  </ol>

  <h3>Phone:</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Call <strong>03-8922 6000</strong></li>
    <li>Follow IVR instructions</li>
    <li>Enter IC number and EPF number</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>In-Person:</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Visit any EPF branch</li>
    <li>Bring your IC</li>
    <li>Request statement at counter or use kiosk</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="dividend-rates">Recent Dividend Rates</h2>
  <table class="w-full border-collapse border border-border my-4">
    <thead>
      <tr class="bg-muted">
        <th class="border border-border p-3 text-left">Year</th>
        <th class="border border-border p-3 text-left">Conventional (%)</th>
        <th class="border border-border p-3 text-left">Shariah (%)</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td class="border border-border p-3">2025</td>
        <td class="border border-border p-3">5.50</td>
        <td class="border border-border p-3">5.40</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td class="border border-border p-3">2024</td>
        <td class="border border-border p-3">5.50</td>
        <td class="border border-border p-3">5.40</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td class="border border-border p-3">2023</td>
        <td class="border border-border p-3">5.35</td>
        <td class="border border-border p-3">5.25</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2 id="important-numbers">Important Contacts & Resources</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>EPF Hotline:</strong> 03-8922 6000</li>
    <li><strong>Toll-Free:</strong> 1-800-88-7080</li>
    <li><strong>WhatsApp:</strong> 017-555 9900</li>
    <li><strong>Website:</strong> epf.gov.my / kwsp.gov.my</li>
    <li><strong>Email:</strong> callcentre@epf.gov.my</li>
    <li><strong>Operating Hours:</strong> Mon-Fri, 8:00 AM - 5:00 PM</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="tips">Tips for Maximizing EPF</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>✅ Check your statement annually</li>
    <li>✅ Update your nominee details</li>
    <li>✅ Consider voluntary contributions for higher retirement savings</li>
    <li>✅ Use Account 3 for emergencies only</li>
    <li>✅ Don't withdraw early unless necessary</li>
    <li>✅ Keep EPF number safe (needed for all transactions)</li>
  </ul>
`;

const faqs = [
  {
    question: "Is EPF mandatory for all workers?",
    answer: "EPF is mandatory for Malaysian citizens and permanent residents employed in Malaysia. Foreign workers can contribute voluntarily. Self-employed individuals can join voluntarily under the i-Saraan program."
  },
  {
    question: "What happens to my EPF if I change jobs?",
    answer: "Your EPF account remains the same. Just provide your EPF number to your new employer. All contributions from different employers go into the same account."
  },
  {
    question: "Can I withdraw EPF if I'm unemployed?",
    answer: "No, unemployment alone is not a valid reason for EPF withdrawal. However, you can withdraw under the Flexible Account (Account 3) if you have funds there."
  },
  {
    question: "How do I nominate beneficiaries for my EPF?",
    answer: "Fill Form KWSP 4 at any EPF branch or update online via i-Akaun. You can nominate multiple beneficiaries and specify percentages. Update nominations after major life events (marriage, birth, death)."
  },
  {
    question: "What is the minimum retirement savings EPF recommends?",
    answer: "EPF recommends having RM240,000 by age 55, which can provide approximately RM1,000 monthly for 20 years. However, the ideal amount depends on your lifestyle expectations."
  }
];

const headings = [
  { id: 'overview', title: 'Overview', level: 2 },
  { id: 'contribution-rates', title: 'Contribution Rates', level: 2 },
  { id: 'account-structure', title: 'Account Structure', level: 2 },
  { id: 'withdrawal-options', title: 'Withdrawal Options', level: 2 },
  { id: 'how-to-check-balance', title: 'How to Check Balance', level: 2 },
  { id: 'dividend-rates', title: 'Dividend Rates', level: 2 },
  { id: 'tips', title: 'Tips for Maximizing EPF', level: 2 },
];
---

<Layout title={`${articleData.articleTitle} | People's Guide | EduLaluan`}>
  <Header />

  <main class="min-h-screen bg-background">
    <!-- Article Header -->
    <section 
      class="relative overflow-hidden py-section-lg border-b"
      style={{
        '--section-color': `rgb(${articleData.colorRgb})`,
        'border-bottom-color': `rgb(${articleData.colorRgb})`
      }}
    >
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="max-w-4xl">
          <!-- Breadcrumb -->
          <Breadcrumb items={[
            { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
            { label: "People's Guide", href: '/panduan-rakyat' },
            { label: `Section ${articleData.sectionNumber}`, href: `/panduan-rakyat/section-${articleData.sectionNumber}` },
            { label: articleData.articleTitle }
          ]} />

          <!-- Back Button -->
          <a
            href={`/panduan-rakyat/section-${articleData.sectionNumber}`}
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-primary transition-colors mb-6"
          >
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7" />
            </svg>
            Back to Section {parseInt(articleData.sectionNumber).toString()}
          </a>

          <!-- Article Title -->
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mt-6">
            <div 
              class="flex h-16 w-16 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-xl text-3xl"
              style={{ 
                'backgroundColor': `rgb(${articleData.colorRgb})`,
                'color': 'white'
              }}
            >
              {articleData.sectionIcon}
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <p class="text-sm font-medium text-primary mb-1 tracking-wide uppercase">
                Section {parseInt(articleData.sectionNumber).toString()}: {articleData.sectionTitle}
              </p>
              <h1 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-foreground">
                {articleData.articleTitle}
              </h1>
              <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground mt-3">
                {articleData.articleDescription}
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Article Content -->
    <section class="py-section-md bg-surface">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="flex gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <!-- Main Content -->
          <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
            <!-- Audience Tabs (Simple/Detailed) -->
            <div class="mb-8">
              <!-- Tab Buttons -->
              <div class="mb-6 flex gap-2 rounded-xl bg-muted p-1.5">
                <button
                  id="tab-simple"
                  class="flex flex-1 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold transition-all duration-200 bg-surface-elevated text-primary shadow-sm"
                  aria-pressed="true"
                  data-tab="simple"
                >
                  <span class="text-xl">🧒</span>
                  <span>Simple</span>
                </button>
                <button
                  id="tab-detailed"
                  class="flex flex-1 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold transition-all duration-200 text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground"
                  aria-pressed="false"
                  data-tab="detailed"
                >
                  <span class="text-xl">🧑</span>
                  <span>Detailed</span>
                </button>
              </div>

              <!-- Tab Content -->
              <div id="content-simple" class="prose-panduan max-w-none tab-content" set:html={simpleContent} />
              <div id="content-detailed" class="prose-panduan max-w-none tab-content hidden" set:html={detailedContent} />
            </div>

            <script is:inline>
              document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
                const tabs = document.querySelectorAll('[data-tab]');
                const contents = {
                  simple: document.getElementById('content-simple'),
                  detailed: document.getElementById('content-detailed')
                };

                tabs.forEach(function(tab) {
                  tab.addEventListener('click', function() {
                    const selectedTab = this.getAttribute('data-tab');
                    
                    tabs.forEach(function(t) {
                      if (t.getAttribute('data-tab') === selectedTab) {
                        t.classList.add('bg-surface-elevated', 'text-primary', 'shadow-sm');
                        t.classList.remove('text-muted-foreground', 'hover:text-foreground');
                        t.setAttribute('aria-pressed', 'true');
                      } else {
                        t.classList.remove('bg-surface-elevated', 'text-primary', 'shadow-sm');
                        t.classList.add('text-muted-foreground', 'hover:text-foreground');
                        t.setAttribute('aria-pressed', 'false');
                      }
                    });

                    if (selectedTab === 'simple') {
                      contents.simple.classList.remove('hidden');
                      contents.detailed.classList.add('hidden');
                    } else {
                      contents.detailed.classList.remove('hidden');
                      contents.simple.classList.add('hidden');
                    }
                  });
                });
              });
            </script>

            <!-- FAQ Section -->
            <div class="mt-12">
              <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-6">
                Frequently Asked Questions
              </h2>
              <div class="space-y-3">
                {faqs.map((faq) => (
                  <details
                    class="group rounded-xl border bg-surface-elevated transition-all"
                  >
                    <summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 font-semibold text-foreground list-none">
                      {faq.question}
                      <svg
                        class="h-5 w-5 text-muted-foreground transition-transform group-open:rotate-180"
                        fill="none"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                      >
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
                      </svg>
                    </summary>
                    <div class="px-5 pb-5 text-muted-foreground">
                      {faq.answer}
                    </div>
                  </details>
                ))}
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Last Updated -->
            <div class="mt-12 pt-6 border-t border-border">
              <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
                <strong>Last updated:</strong> {articleData.lastUpdated}
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Table of Contents (Sidebar) -->
          <aside class="sticky top-24 hidden lg:block w-64 shrink-0">
            <nav class="space-y-1" aria-label="Table of contents">
              <h3 class="text-xs font-semibold text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">
                On This Page
              </h3>
              {headings.map((heading) => (
                <a
                  href={`#${heading.id}`}
                  class="block py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground transition-colors"
                  style={{ paddingLeft: `${(heading.level - 2) * 12 + 12}px` }}
                >
                  {heading.title}
                </a>
              ))}
            </nav>
          </aside>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Navigation Footer -->
    <section class="py-section-md bg-background">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
          <div class="rounded-2xl border bg-surface-elevated p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-muted-foreground">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
              <p class="text-sm">
                <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> This guide provides general information only. Always verify with official sources for the most current information.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Section padding utilities */
  :root {
    --section-padding-lg: clamp(3rem, 5vw + 1rem, 5rem);
    --section-padding-md: clamp(2rem, 3vw + 1rem, 3rem);
  }

  .py-section-lg {
    padding-top: var(--section-padding-lg);
    padding-bottom: var(--section-padding-lg);
  }

  .py-section-md {
    padding-top: var(--section-padding-md);
    padding-bottom: var(--section-padding-md);
  }

  /* Article Typography */
  .prose-panduan {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--foreground);
  }

  .prose-panduan h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--foreground);
  }

  .prose-panduan h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--foreground);
  }

  .prose-panduan p {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .prose-panduan ul,
  .prose-panduan ol {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .prose-panduan li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .prose-panduan a {
    color: var(--primary);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .prose-panduan a:hover {
    color: var(--primary-dark);
  }

  .prose-panduan strong {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--foreground);
  }

  .prose-panduan table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .prose-panduan th {
    background-color: var(--muted);
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .prose-panduan td {
    padding: 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .prose-panduan .bg-muted {
    background-color: var(--muted);
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }
</style>
